    }

}
```

Here are a some additional un-related recommendations.

Optionally, just use  _&quot;src/files/80stoyota.csv&quot;_.\
The _[File](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/io/File.html#%3Cinit%3E(java.lang.String))_ class infers a relative path.

Use the _[Scanner](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/util/Scanner.html)_ class, instead of _BufferedReader_.

```java
try(Scanner in = new Scanner(new File(&quot;src/files/80stoyota.csv&quot;)))
```

And, use a _[record class](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/language/records.html)_ instead of a _class_.
